\int_{I_{i}}\left(\partial_{t}u^{h}\right)v^{h}\dd{x}+\int_{I_{i}}\left(\partial_{x}u^{h}\right)\left(\partial_{x}v^{h}\right)\dd{x}=\left.\widehat{\partial_{x}u^{h}}\,v^{h}\right|_{x_{i-1/2}}^{x_{i+1/2}}
